nk {{in lang|fr}} (Vive La Compagnie)\n|LineColor=7B26CA\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|Title=Stop and Smell Up the Flowers / Firehouse Frolics\n|OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|10|16}}\n|EpisodeNumber=53\n|EpisodeNumber2=13\n|ShortSummary=Pepe tours the babies around the Acme gardens finding a place to plant a lemon tree. Eventually everyone gets irritated by Pepe's stink, upsetting him, but they rejoin him and he introduces them to his pal [[Gossamer (Looney Tunes)|Gossamer]].\n\n''Song'': Loonies Turn Around (Windmills Turn Around)\n\nFloyd takes the babies to the fire station where Captain Frank tutors them on safety procedures, but Daffy won't follow the rules. However Daffy's morale in the situation of a fire is higher than all the others.\n'''Note''': This is the series finale.\n\n|LineColor=7B26CA\n}}\n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:List of Baby Looney Tunes episodes}}\n[[Category:Lists of American children's animated television series episodes|Baby Looney Tunes]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Baby Looney Tunes'' episodes}}\n{{unreferenced|date=June 2012}}\n{{Disputed|what=Article has been subject to pervasive date vandalism, so most of the article's listed air dates are incorrect \u2013 see the Amazon entry for this series for the correct dates \u2013 as a result, this article|date=July 2019}}\nThis is a list of episodes of the [[United States|American]] [[animated television series]] ''[[Baby Looney Tunes]]''.\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n| color1    = FFFFBF\n| link1     = <includeonly>List of Baby Looney Tunes episodes</includeonly>#Season 1 (2001)\n| episodes1 = 38\n| start1    = {{Start date|2001|6|3}}\n| end1      = {{End date|2003|3|21}}\n| network1  = [[Kids' WB]] and [[Cartoon Network]]\n\n| color1S   = cccccc\n| link1S    = <includeonly>List of Baby Looney Tunes episodes</includeonly>#Movie Specials (2003)\n| linkT1S   = Movie Specials\n| start1S   